Hello, /Collared/ !
Welcome to my Pokémon Sexual Analysis (PSA)! I am Professor Harkness!
In each of my PSA’s, we will be looking at, and ranking, a particular Pokémon’s sexual capabilities, as well as some tips and tricks on taming Pokémon. For my first PSA, we’ll be looking at Pokémon number 001, Bulbasaur!
