>QOTT: Are all anthros equal in your imagined collared setting, or are some sub-species more equal than others?

>QOTT
Since Humans exist as a sort of ubermensch class that guarantees even the lowest human is still above most anthros, that leaves anthros to make up the other 99% of the social ladder. The easiest way for an anthro to gain status is by riding the coattails [read: dick] of a human. Being a human's mate is the highest class of anthro, supplemented only by bearing a human child. Most anthros at this level of society are the ones humans like best. Personal taste accounts for a lot, but it trends that most are canines, vulpines, and felines. Though rabbits, scalies, avian, and the occasional horse also exist here.
Then comes the indirect family structure. Friends, personal attendants, and favored servants. Anthros in these positions often vie for a human's attentions in an attempt to raise their stature to the top level. Most anthro politicians also exist at this level, since most of them are overseen by humans, either human political leaders or in the pockets of human businesses. These are most species that humans tend to like. Basically anything a human finds pleasant can exist here, depending on the tastes of the individual human.
Then comes the service class. Those in direct employ of a human, or owners of businesses that serve human clientele. Most businesses employ cute and cuddly to draw a human's eye, but the more exotic races are sometimes hired as a draw.
Below that, the working class. The average anthro going about their day that probably doesn't have a hope of seeing a human, let alone talking to one. Most of the population exists at this level. 80% of the population lives here, so you can find just about any type of species among the working class.
Then the lower classes. The poor, the fringe, and the criminal. As well as anything humans tend to reject. Wasp girls live here, also most furbois.
Then at the very bottom are the anti-humanists. Criminal anthros who have fallen for anti-human rhetoric and reject human superiority. Require reeducation.

