Offer them an opportunity to serve humans, earn money and live a pleasant life, but be careful about accepting too many anthros or in general about who you accept. You don't want to drive the local anthro settlements into extinction by deporting them all. And you also don't want to genetically cripple them by just taking all the pretty ones for yourself and leaving all the ugly ones.
Care should also be made about the male to female ratio and it is recommended to organize at least a once a decade convoy to snatch up all the ugly female anthros and as many males as possible, since anthros will steadily adopt polygamy in case of a lack of males.

