As for leaving some of the pretty behind and take the "uglies" sto ensure the beauty of the enxt generation, that is especially true when it comes to pure-stock. It's a balance that Mankind have taken upon its shoulders.
Also, "ugly" is a relative term. There's always someone who's interested, even if only for the novilty, so if you got problems selling your existing stock,try transporting them to another market further away where their species is less common. That usually works.
